<p>This shows us that we need to add values to the dictionary before we can continue. The task also specifies that we shouldnâ€™t just reassign the emails variable. Hereâ€™s an example solution to this:</p>

<p><strong>using-dictionaries.py</strong> (partial)</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code># 2) Add 'ashley', 'craig', and 'elizabeth' to the emails dictionary without reassigning the variable.

